Author: Aman Karunakaran
Maintainer: Aman Karunakaran
Version: 1.0
Description: AI to play word game “ghost”. Rules can be found at https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ghost_(game). Minimum valid word length is 3 letters.
Usage: Type ‘./ghost’ into terminal, without quotes. Program only supports two players right now, but should play perfectly in that case. To challenge, type ‘?’ without quotes when prompted for a letter.
Notes: Dictionary used is Mac OS X file words.txt. If you want to use your own, then create a file with all desired words named ‘words.txt’. Note that words with any capital letters are thrown out.